overview: Reborn: Completion was a wrestling event promoted by Ring of Honor. It took place on July 17, 2004 at the Rex Plex in Elizabeth, New Jersey. It featured a main event of ROH World Champion Samoa Joe & the Briscoe Brothers taking on The Rottweilers: Homicide, Ricky Reyes & Rocky Romero.
title: ROH: Reborn - Completion
